thoughts.reasoning_problem:

SelectiveBreeding(heckCattle, aurochs) ::: Heck cattle were bred-back in the 1920s to resemble the aurochs.
Animal(heckCattle) ::: Heck cattle are animals.
Animal(aurochs) ::: Aurochs are animals.
∃x (Animal(x) ∧ ResembleExtinct(x)) ::: Some animals to be bred-back resemble animals that are extinct.
Conclusion:
∃x (Animal(x) ∧ ¬Animal(x)) ::: Aurochs are extinct.
